Class OrderImportBuilder

java.lang.Object
com.commercetools.importapi.models.orders.OrderImportBuilder
All Implemented Interfaces:
Builder<OrderImport>
public class OrderImportBuilder extends Object implements Builder<OrderImport>
OrderImportBuilder
Example to create an instance using the builder pattern 

     OrderImport orderImport = OrderImport.builder()
             .orderNumber("{orderNumber}")
             .totalPrice(totalPriceBuilder -> totalPriceBuilder)
             .build()
